com.vgrs.xcode.cmdline.common
Class UnicodeCmdLine

java.lang.Object
  com.vgrs.xcode.cmdline.CmdLine
      com.vgrs.xcode.cmdline.common.UnicodeCmdLine

public class UnicodeCmdLine
extends CmdLine

This class converts between Unicode data and Utf-16 using the surrogate arithmetic specified in the UTF-16 RFC.

  • Usage: com.vgrs.xcode.cmdline.common.UnicodeCmdLine (--encode | --decode) file=[file name]
  • Input type: Utf-16 for encode, Unicode for decode
  • Output type: Unicode for encode, Utf-16 for decode

Version:
1.0 Aug 10, 2010
Author:
nchigurupati
